<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5377563>
    dc:description "Figs. 2–5. Amithao species. 2) Short, blunt mesometasternal process (lateral view) of A. cotopaxicus; 3) Caudal view and 4) Lateral view of parameres of A. cotopaxicus; 5) Example of slender, attenuate, mesometasternal process (lateral view) as seen in A. haematopus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5377563/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

